title: How Did Liv Get Pregnant? American Horror Stories Theory Video
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: In my opinion it's more simple: since her husband and his friends wanted her to think the totem was real, he stopped doing his infertile method which allowed her to get pregnant. Then Liv actually summoned Ba'al later once her husband's mistress gave her that spell. To me that makes more sense because in order for her husband and Co to convince Liv the totem was real, they needed to insure she got pregnant when she got it.
